Supreme Court of India
State Of West Bengal And Ors. vs Mohurgong And Gulma Tea Estates ... on 5 May, 1988Equivalent citations: AIR 1988 SC 1450, JT 1988 (2) SC 592, 1988 (1) SCALE 884 a, 1988 Supp (1) SCC 340
Bench: R Pathak, K X M.H.
ORDER 
  

1. We see no reason for the transfer of these matters to this Court. The High Court concerned can dispose of the petitions in the light of our decision in Writ Petitions Nos. 5409-10 of 1980 (Tata Tea Co. Limited and Anr. v. State of West Bengal and Ors. connected Writ Petitions. These Transfer Petitions are, therefore, rejected.

2. There will be no order as to costs.

